// SoA Benchmark (llmlang) - High Precision
# Vector id x y z

: init_loop i v c
    ? < ⚓ i ⚓ c
        . S ⚓ v id ⚓ i ⚓ i
        . S ⚓ v x ⚓ i 1
        . S ⚓ v y ⚓ i 2
        . S ⚓ v z ⚓ i 3
        @3 init_loop + ⚓ i 1 ⚓ v ⚓ c
        0

: sum_loop i v c acc
    ? < ⚓ i ⚓ c
        @4 sum_loop + ⚓ i 1 ⚓ v ⚓ c + ⚓ acc G ⚓ v x ⚓ i
        ⚓ acc

: main
    L count 10000000
    L v N Vector ⚓ count
    
    L start_init 🕒⌛
    . @3 init_loop 0 ⚓ v ⚓ count
    L end_init 🕒⌛
    . 📤 1 ⧉ "Init Time: " ⧉ 🧵 / - ⚓ end_init ⚓ start_init 1000000 "ms\n"

    L start_sum 🕒⌛
    L total @4 sum_loop 0 ⚓ v ⚓ count 0
    L end_sum 🕒⌛
    
    . 📤 1 ⧉ "Sum: " ⧉ 🧵 ⮞ total "\n"
    . 📤 1 ⧉ "Sum Time: " ⧉ 🧵 / - ⚓ end_sum ⚓ start_sum 1000000 "ms\n"
    
    0
